# Universal Search & Chat Revamp Implementation Plan

The goal is to enable "Universal Search" where the system searches both the web (Google) and the local graph (RAG) to answer user queries, populating the canvas with relevant external information.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> This introduces a new "Universal Search" toggle in the Chat Interface. When enabled, queries will take longer as they perform a real-time web search.

